trans-unit.source: Contains a collection of <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfo"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en samling av <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfo"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: The TransformerInfoCollection class allows you to programmatically access and modify the `transformers` section of the `webParts` section of a configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Klassen TransformerInfoCollection gjør det mulig å programmatisk tilgang til og endre den `transformers` delen av den `webParts` delen av konfigurasjonsfilen.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfo> objects, as part of a TransformerInfoCollection, specify custom classes that extend the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> class.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfo>objekter angi som en del av en TransformerInfoCollection egendefinerte klasser som utvider <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer>klasse.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer></xref:System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfo>

trans-unit.source: These transformer classes act as bridges between connected Web Parts, translating data sent by a connection provider into something that the connection consumer can accept.
trans-unit.target: Disse klassene transformeringen fungerer som broer mellom tilkoblede webdeler, sendt oversette data av en tilkoblingsleverandør av til noe tilkoblingen forbrukeren godtar.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfoCollection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfoCollection"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The TransformerInfoCollection constructor is not intended to be used directly from your code.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren TransformerInfoCollection skal ikke brukes direkte fra koden.

trans-unit.source: It is called by the ASP.NET configuration system.
trans-unit.target: Kalles av ASP.NET Konfigurasjonssystemet.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Configuration.WebPartsSection.Transformers%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.WebPartsSection> class always contains an instance of the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfoCollection> type.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.Configuration.WebPartsSection.Transformers%2A>for den <xref:System.Web.Configuration.WebPartsSection>klassen alltid inneholder en forekomst av den <xref:System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfoCollection>type.</xref:System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfoCollection> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.WebPartsSection> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.WebPartsSection.Transformers%2A>

trans-unit.source: Use this instance, rather than creating your own.
trans-unit.target: Bruk denne forekomsten i stedet for å opprette din egen.
